{
  "stem": "4189.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "An SS guard came out and saw who it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He called out the butchers there, the prisoners that were working there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took the two kettles inside, they filled them up, and then they brought them out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he helped me put them back on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I went back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- and that's the water-- that water they gave to these unfortunate people that were working so hard on those hot presses, where they had to-- with hot-- with tongs, they had to bring out the hot metal that was fire-- fire red.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we wanted to figure out a way-- how could we bring out some of those sausages from that kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had a meeting in the camp, with the butchers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we devised a plan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the factory where I worked, in the machine shop, we also had a tinsmith shop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The tinsmith shop manufactured a double bottom for those kettles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we put-- when I brought the kettles to the kitchen, the butchers put some sausages into the-- into the bottom.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then put the false bottom on top of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In this way, I was able to bring that back to the factory there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this went on for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Until, one day, another fellow-- Max was his name-- he said to me, I want to go with you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because you're also going to the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was another job that I had to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At the same time that I went to the kitchen, I also had to stop by the camp, by the main gate of the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had to give them sheets of all the names of the people that worked in the factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
